{
  "stem": "7598.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And we talked about what would be happening next.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I don't think we shared our anguish and fears.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think we all, children and others, kept this very much to ourselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And also I was a child of a generation where children were, you know, seen and not heard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If my parents discussed these things at night, which I'm sure they did, we really didn't join in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My brother, I'm sure, was more involved than I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] All I know is that one morning about a week after we got there, my father said it was time to try and get to Cognac.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We rented a car to cross the frontier.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father was going to ferry his family backwards and forwards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In one car, his parents and my other grandparents went and crossed the border.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The car came back, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in one of them there was my uncle, that is to say, my father's brother and his wife, his two daughters-- and it was a very large [INAUDIBLE]-- my mother, my brother, and myself.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My father was a big man.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was tall and quite robust.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he really couldn't get in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And my mother said, well, don't worry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'll go across the frontier with the children, and then I'll come back for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We got to the frontier that night, and the French were very unpleasant.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They said that the Belgians weren't really fighting very hard.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "The irony of it is that Belgium capitulated within two weeks and France within three weeks.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But, of course, no one was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "There was chaos and there was panic.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
